strings.Value: "Well, well, what have we here?" {n}Octavia flips through the pages of one of the books.{/n} "Reg! Take a look at this!"
"What is it? Whoa! By {g|Calistria}Calistria's{/g} tits, this is… Ha ha! Hmmm, found something interesting here!"
"Right, yes! We'll just be taking these books, I think. Do you have any idea what this is?"

{n}Octavia triumphantly points at a page of a thick volume.{/n} "These are the Maestro's ledgers! All his accounting for the last… let's see, ten, twenty… Yes! For the last thirty years! Do you know what this means?"
"Somewhere in these pages is me and Octavia. When we were bought, for how much, from where… maybe even from who!"

"It'll take some time to make sense of the ledger. We may not find anything… or we may find something and regret ever looking. But I still want to know the truth. I want to understand who I am and where I come from."
"Looks like the old geezer left us something valuable!"
"The Maestro was in such a hurry to leave that he left something pretty interesting behind!"

"I'm not all that interested in my tribe, really… I already know who they are — piles of shit who sell their children into slavery! But it might still be interesting to pay them a visit, maybe spit into their faces personally."
"Some value! I thought you found some work notes, or research results... Well, everyone has their own idea of value, I guess!"
"Accou...what? Sounds boring! No treasure maps? Not even a little one?"
"How do you not understand? It means... This is..."
